overview: Tesseract is innovative business analytics software for fact-based decision making that is simple, powerful, and cost-effective. Tesseract combines all of the tools required to move from data to decisions into a single frictionless solution. Powerful analytics, insightful dashboards, and flexible reports are all supported by a unified view of information no matter where it resides. Tesseract enables businesses to make prompt decisions and take immediate action.
